'''Bold Pilot''' ( April 21, 1993 – April 30, 2015) is a [[Turkey|Turkish]] [[thoroughbred]] [[racehorse]]. He was sired by [[Persian Bold]] and owned by [[Özdemir Atman]]. He won eight of the nine races including the race [[Gazi Derby]], as a three-year-old. He set a track record in the 1996 Gazi Derby recording a time of 2.26.22. He won sixteen of twenty one races.<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QOTwSXThwb4</ref> Bold Pilot died 30 April 2015 in Istanbul.<ref>http://www.radikal.com.tr/spor/efsane_at_bold_pilot_oldu-1346648</ref>
