[[File:Browhaus, 56 Neal Street, Covent Garden 01.jpg|thumb|''Browhaus'', Neal Street, [[Covent Garden]], London]]
'''Browhaus''' is a [[Singapore]]an eyebrow and eyelash grooming chain

Browhaus was founded in  Singapore in 2004, and as of 2016, has 31 eyebrow and eyelash grooming outlets with 31 outlets in nine cities: Singapore, [[London]], [[New York City|New York]], [[Shanghai]], [[Hong Kong]], [[Manila]], [[Jakarta]], [[Bangkok]], and [[Kuala Lumpur]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.browhaus.com/ |title=Browhaus |publisher=Browhaus |date= |accessdate=21 February 2016}}</ref>

Browhaus offers "brow resurrection", using temporary tattoos to create the illusion of larger eyebrows.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vogue.co.uk/beauty/2013/05/02/cara-delevingne-brows-at-browhaus-covent-garden |title=Cara Delevingne Brows At Browhaus Covent Garden |website=Vogue.co.uk |date= |accessdate=21 February 2016}}</ref>

